<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Common in West and Central Africa but a recent introduction in the neotropics in a Colombian oil palm plantation.</paragraph>
